[2026-05-19T01:13:17.676Z] [STDOUT] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_function_n44517t5bgfq_1","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Mood & Wellness — Screen Specification\n2\t\n3\t## 1. Screen Title\n4\t\n5\t**Mood & Wellness**\n6\t\n7\t---\n8\t\n9\t## 2. Purpose\n10\t\n11\tLog daily moods and energy levels, visualize patterns over a 7-day trend, and receive contextual wellness recommendations. The screen serves as a dedicated space for emotional self-awareness during pregnancy — empowering mothers to track and understand their mental and physical energy patterns over time.\n12\t\n13\t---\n14\t\n15\t## 3. Route\n16\t\n17\t```\n18\t/mood-wellness\n19\t```\n20\t\n21\t**Parent Navigation:** Library tab (push route)\n22\t\n23\t---\n24\t\n25\t## 4. Widget Name\n26\t\n27\t```dart\n28\tMoodWellnessScreen\n29\t```\n30\t\n31\t---\n32\t\n33\t## 5. Design Tokens\n34\t\n35\t### Color Palette (from DESIGN.md)\n36\t\n37\t| Token | Hex | Usage |\n38\t|---|---|---|\n39\t| `lavenderBloom` | `#7C3AED` | Primary brand, AppBar, chart lines |\n40\t| `blushRose` | `#F9A8D4` | Mood emoji highlights, secondary accents |\n41\t| `softMint` | `#6EE7B7` | Positive indicators, high energy states |\n42\t| `morningMist` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n43\t| `lavenderTint` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background |\n44\t| `deepGraphite` | `#1F2937` | Primary text |\n45\t| `stoneGrey` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, captions |\n46\t| `mistyBorder` | `#E5E7EB` | Dividers, subtle structure |\n47\t| `softCoral` | `#EF4444` | Error states |\n48\t\n49\t### Typography (Nunito — Google Fonts)\n50\t\n51\t| Style | Size | Weight | Usage |\n52\t|---|---|---|---|\n53\t| `headlineMedium` | 24sp | 700 | Screen title |\n54\t| `titleLarge` | 20sp | 600 | Section headers |\n55\t| `titleMedium` | 16sp | 600 | Card titles |\n56\t| `bodyLarge` | 16sp | 400 | Primary body text |\n57\t| `bodyMedium` | 14sp | 400 | Secondary text, notes |\n58\t| `labelLarge` | 14sp | 600 | Button labels, chip text |\n59\t| `caption` | 12sp | 400 | Timestamps, metadata |\n60\t\n61\t### Spacing (8pt base grid)\n62\t\n63\t| Token | Value |\n64\t|---|---|\n65\t| `xxs` | 4dp |\n66\t| `xs` | 8dp |\n67\t| `sm` | 12dp |\n68\t| `md` | 16dp |\n69\t| `lg` | 24dp |\n70\t| `xl` | 32dp |\n71\t\n72\t### Corner Radius\n73\t\n74\t| Token | Value |\n75\t|---|---|\n76\t| `sm` | 8dp |\n77\t| `md` | 12dp |\n78\t| `lg` | 16dp |\n79\t| `full` | 999dp (pills) |\n80\t\n81\t---\n82\t\n83\t## 6. Layout Rules\n84\t\n85\t### Scaffold Structure\n86\t\n87\t```\n88\tMoodWellnessScreen\n89\t├── AppBar (\"Mood & Wellness\", back button, transparent/lavender tint bg)\n90\t├── body: CustomScrollView\n91\t│   ├── SliverAppBar (collapsible, pinned)\n92\t│   │   └── Today's Mood Card (expanded height ~280dp)\n93\t│   └── SliverToBoxAdapter\n94\t│       ├── Mood Trend Chart Section\n95\t│       ├── Energy Trend Chart Section\n96\t│       └── Wellness Tip Section\n97\t└── BottomNavigationBar: Hidden\n98\t```\n99\t\n100\t### AppBar Behavior\n101\t\n102\t- **Title:** \"Mood & Wellness\", SemiBold 20pt, deepGraphite\n103\t- **Leading:** Back arrow (IconButton, 48pt touch target)\n104\t- **Background:** Transparent, blends into lavenderTint scaffold\n105\t- **Scroll behavior:** SliverAppBar collapses on scroll; title remains visible\n106\t\n107\t### Body\n108\t\n109\t- `CustomScrollView` with `SliverAppBar` (no FAB per UX spec)\n110\t- `SliverToBoxAdapter` wraps remaining sections below the collapsible header\n111\t- Each section separated by 24dp vertical spacing\n112\t\n113\t### Bottom Navigation\n114\t\n115\t- **Hidden** on this screen (per UX.md 3.7)\n116\t- Screen is reached via push route from Library tab\n117\t\n118\t---\n119\t\n120\t## 7. Sections\n121\t\n122\t### Section 1: Today's Mood Card\n123\t\n124\t**Description:** Large card with 5 emoji mood selectors in a horizontal row and an optional note field. The card serves as the primary interaction point for logging today's mood.\n125\t\n126\t**Widget Type:** `SliverAppBar` expanded child (Container card)\n127\t\n128\t**Layout:**\n129\t```\n130\tCard (rounded 16dp, morningMist bg, soft shadow)\n131\t├── Header row: \"How are you feeling today?\" title + date\n132\t├── Emoji row: 5 emoji buttons (😔 😕 😐 🙂 😊) evenly spaced\n133\t├── Selected indicator: highlighted emoji with blushRose border\n134\t└── Note field: optional TextField for context\n135\t```\n136\t\n137\t**Emoji Mapping:**\n138\t| Emoji | Mood Score | Label |\n139\t|---|---|---|\n140\t| 😔 | 1 | Terrible |\n141\t| 😕 | 2 | Bad |\n142\t| 😐 | 3 | Okay |\n143\t| 🙂 | 4 | Good |\n144\t| 😊 | 5 | Great |\n145\t\n146\t**Data Requirements:**\n147\t- Reads `todayMood` from `MoodEntryProvider`\n148\t- Writes new mood log on emoji tap via `MoodEntryProvider.logMood(score)`\n149\t- If mood already logged today, show the selected emoji pre-highlighted\n150\t\n151\t**Interactive Elements:**\n152\t- Tap emoji → `MoodEntryProvider.logMood(score)` + visual highlight\n153\t- Tap note field → expands for text input (max 200 characters)\n154\t- Tap outside deselects note field\n155\t\n156\t**States:**\n157\t- **Default:** No mood logged today, all emojis neutral\n158\t- **Logged:** Selected emoji highlighted with blushRose border and subtle scale\n159\t- **Loading:** Emoji tap shows 200ms ripple before confirmation\n160\t\n161\t---\n162\t\n163\t### Section 2: Mood Trend Chart\n164\t\n165\t**Description:** Line chart showing 7-day mood score history. The chart is interactive — tapping a data point reveals a bottom sheet with that day's details.\n166\t\n167\t**Widget Type:** CustomPaint line chart inside a Card container\n168\t\n169\t**Layout:**\n170\t```\n171\tCard (rounded 16dp, morningMist bg)\n172\t├── Section header: \"Mood Trend\" + toggle chips (1W / 1M / All)\n173\t├── Chart area: 200dp height, CustomPaint line chart\n174\t│   ├── X-axis: 7 day labels (Mon, Tue, Wed, etc.)\n175\t│   ├── Y-axis: 1-5 scale with emoji labels\n176\t│   └── Line: lavenderBloom colored, 2dp stroke, smooth curve\n177\t├── Legend: \"Score\" label + 5-dot color guide\n178\t└── Tap target: entire chart is tappable\n179\t```\n180\t\n181\t**Data Requirements:**\n182\t- Reads `MoodEntryProvider.entries` last 7 days (filtered by `date`)\n183\t- Mood scores 1-5 mapped to emoji at Y-axis positions\n184\t- Data points connected with smooth bezier curves\n185\t\n186\t**Toggle Behavior:**\n187\t- `1W` — Last 7 days (default)\n188\t- `1M` — Last 30 days (shows more data points)\n189\t- `All` — All historical entries\n190\t- Active toggle has lavenderBloom bg at 15% opacity\n191\t\n192\t**Interactive Elements:**\n193\t- Tap data point → bottom sheet with day detail (date, mood score, emoji, note if exists)\n194\t- Toggle chip tap → re-renders chart with new time range\n195\t\n196\t**Chart Style:**\n197\t- Line color: `lavenderBloom` (#7C3AED)\n198\t- Line stroke: 2dp\n199\t- Data point dots: 6dp circles at each entry\n200\t- Empty state: \"No mood data yet\" centered text\n201\t\n202\t---\n203\t\n204\t### Section 3: Energy Trend Chart\n205\t\n206\t**Description:** Line chart showing 7-day energy level history. Structure mirrors the Mood Trend Chart but tracks energy instead of mood.\n207\t\n208\t**Widget Type:** CustomPaint line chart inside a Card container\n209\t\n210\t**Layout:**\n211\t```\n212\tCard (rounded 16dp, morningMist bg)\n213\t├── Section header: \"Energy Trend\" + toggle chips (1W / 1M / All)\n214\t├── Chart area: 200dp height, CustomPaint line chart\n215\t│   ├── X-axis: 7 day labels\n216\t│   ├── Y-axis: 1-5 scale with energy descriptors\n217\t│   └── Line: softMint (#6EE7B7) colored, 2dp stroke\n218\t├── Legend: \"Energy\" label + 5-dot color guide\n219\t└── Tap target: entire chart is tappable\n220\t```\n221\t\n222\t**Data Requirements:**\n223\t- Reads `MoodEntryProvider.entries` last 7 days\n224\t- Energy levels 1-5 mapped to descriptors at Y-axis positions\n225\t\n226\t**Y-Axis Labels:**\n227\t| Score | Label |\n228\t|---|---|\n229\t| 1 | Very Low |\n230\t| 2 | Low |\n231\t| 3 | Moderate |\n232\t| 4 | High |\n233\t| 5 | Very High |\n234\t\n235\t**Interactive Elements:**\n236\t- Tap data point → bottom sheet with day detail (date, energy level, note if exists)\n237\t- Toggle chip tap → re-renders chart with new time range\n238\t\n239\t**Chart Style:**\n240\t- Line color: `softMint` (#6EE7B7)\n241\t- Line stroke: 2dp\n242\t- Data point dots: 6dp circles\n243\t\n244\t---\n245\t\n246\t### Section 4: Wellness Tip\n247\t\n248\t**Description:** Contextual recommendation card that analyzes recent mood/energy patterns and suggests a gentle wellness nudge.\n249\t\n250\t**Widget Type:** Card with expandable content\n251\t\n252\t**Layout:**\n253\t```\n254\tCard (rounded 16dp, morningMist bg)\n255\t├── Header row: \"Wellness Tip\" title + lightbulb icon\n256\t├── Tip text: Contextual recommendation (2-3 sentences)\n257\t├── Category badge: \"Mood\" / \"Energy\" / \"General\" chip\n258\t└── Expand trigger: Tap anywhere on card to expand\n259\t```\n260\t\n261\t**Tip Generation Logic (Rule-Based):**\n262\t- If average mood < 3 over past 7 days → \"Your mood has been low lately. Consider a gentle breathing exercise or a short walk outside.\"\n263\t- If average energy < 3 over past 7 days → \"Your energy levels seem to be dipping. Remember to stay hydrated and take short breaks throughout the day.\"\n264\t- If mood is high but energy is low → \"You've been feeling good emotionally, but energy is lagging. Listen to your body and rest when needed.\"\n265\t- Default → \"Regular mood check-ins help you notice patterns. Keep up the great work tracking your wellness!\"\n266\t\n267\t**Data Requirements:**\n268\t- Reads `MoodEntryProvider.entries` last 7 days\n269\t- Computes average moodScore and average energyLevel\n270\t- Selects appropriate tip from static catalog\n271\t\n272\t**Interactive Elements:**\n273\t- Tap card → expands to show full recommendation (up to 100 characters additional detail)\n274\t- Tap category badge → no action (informational only)\n275\t\n276\t**States:**\n277\t- **Collapsed:** Shows tip preview (max 2 lines)\n278\t- **Expanded:** Shows full tip text with additional context\n279\t- **No Data:** Shows generic tip \"Log your mood to receive personalized wellness tips.\"\n280\t\n281\t---\n282\t\n283\t## 8. Data\n284\t\n285\t### Entity: MoodEntry\n286\t\n287\t```dart\n288\tclass MoodEntry {\n289\t  final DateTime date;\n290\t  final int moodScore;    // 1-5 scale\n291\t  final int energyLevel;  // 1-5 scale\n292\t  final String? note;\n293\t}\n294\t```\n295\t\n296\t### Provider: MoodEntryProvider\n297\t\n298\t**Read Operations:**\n299\t- `todayMood` → MoodEntry? — Today's mood entry (if exists)\n300\t- `entries` → List<MoodEntry> — All mood entries sorted by date\n301\t- `entriesInRange(start, end)` → List<MoodEntry> — Entries within date range\n302\t\n303\t**Write Operations:**\n304\t- `logMood(int score)` → void — Logs/updates today's mood score\n305\t- `logEnergy(int level)` → void — Logs/updates today's energy level\n306\t- `addNote(String note)` → void — Adds/updates note for today\n307\t\n308\t### Screen Data Dependencies\n309\t\n310\t| Section | Data Source | Fields Used |\n311\t|---|---|---|\n312\t| Today's Mood Card | `MoodEntryProvider.todayMood` | `moodScore`, `note` |\n313\t| Mood Trend Chart | `MoodEntryProvider.entriesInRange` | `date`, `moodScore` |\n314\t| Energy Trend Chart | `MoodEntryProvider.entriesInRange` | `date`, `energyLevel` |\n315\t| Wellness Tip | `MoodEntryProvider.entries` (last 7 days) | `moodScore`, `energyLevel` |\n316\t\n317\t---\n318\t\n319\t## 9. Motion\n320\t\n321\t### Entry Animations\n322\t\n323\t| Element | Animation | Duration | Curve |\n324\t|---|---|---|---|\n325\t| Today's Mood Card | Fade + slide up | 300ms | easeOut |\n326\t| Mood Trend Chart | Fade + slide up (staggered 50ms after card) | 300ms | easeOut |\n327\t| Energy Trend Chart | Fade + slide up (staggered 50ms after mood chart) | 300ms | easeOut |\n328\t| Wellness Tip | Fade + slide up (staggered 50ms after energy chart) | 300ms | easeOut |\n329\t\n330\t### Micro-Interactions\n331\t\n332\t| Interaction | Animation | Duration | Curve |\n333\t|---|---|---|---|\n334\t| Emoji tap | Scale to 95% + color fill | 200ms | easeOut |\n335\t| Toggle chip select | Background color fade | 150ms | easeInOut |\n336\t| Card expand | Height + content fade | 250ms | easeInOut |\n337\t| Chart data point tap | Scale pulse on dot | 200ms | easeOut |\n338\t\n339\t### Page Transitions\n340\t\n341\t- **Enter:** Push from Library tab — 300ms slide from right + fade\n342\t- **Exit:** Swipe-back or back button — 300ms slide to right + fade\n343\t\n344\t---\n345\t\n346\t## 10. Accessibility\n347\t\n348\t### Semantics Labels\n349\t\n350\t| Element | Semantics Label |\n351\t|---|---|\n352\t| Mood emoji 😔 | \"Terrible mood, tap to log\" |\n353\t| Mood emoji 😕 | \"Bad mood, tap to log\" |\n354\t| Mood emoji 😐 | \"Okay mood, tap to log\" |\n355\t| Mood emoji 🙂 | \"Good mood, tap to log\" |\n356\t| Mood emoji 😊 | \"Great mood, tap to log\" |\n357\t| Mood chart | \"Mood trend chart showing 7 day history\" |\n358\t| Energy chart | \"Energy trend chart showing 7 day history\" |\n359\t| Wellness tip card | \"Wellness tip: [tip text]\" |\n360\t\n361\t### Focus Order\n362\t\n363\t1. AppBar back button\n364\t2. Today's Mood Card emoji buttons (left to right: 😔 😕 😐 🙂 😊)\n365\t3. Note text field\n366\t4. Mood chart toggle chips\n367\t5. Energy chart toggle chips\n368\t6. Wellness tip card\n369\t\n370\t### Contrast Notes\n371\t\n372\t- All text meets WCAG AA contrast (4.5:1 for body, 3:1 for large text)\n373\t- Emoji buttons have 48pt minimum touch targets\n374\t- Chart lines use lavenderBloom on morningMist — sufficient contrast\n375\t- Focus indicators use 2dp blushRose outline\n376\t\n377\t---\n378\t\n379\t## 11. Anti-Patterns\n380\t\n381\t**DO NOT:**\n382\t- Use default Flutter colors — all colors from design token palette\n383\t- Add a FAB — this screen has no FAB per UX spec\n384\t- Show BottomNavigationBar — it is hidden\n385\t- Use sharp corners — all cards use 16dp radius\n386\t- Display raw numbers on chart axes — use emoji/text labels\n387\t- Use Inter or Roboto — Nunito only\n388\t- Show gradients — flat colors only\n389\t- Use touch targets smaller than 48pt\n390\t- Place critical actions outside thumb zone"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1c41826a-32c6-4b33-bffb-c77c405449e9","uuid":"c891530b-3dcf-4177-83b2-8198b6beb7ac","timestamp":"2026-05-19T01:13:17.676Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.stitch/designs/mood-wellness/SPEC.md","content":"# Mood & Wellness — Screen Specification\n\n## 1. Screen Title\n\n**Mood & Wellness**\n\n---\n\n## 2. Purpose\n\nLog daily moods and energy levels, visualize patterns over a 7-day trend, and receive contextual wellness recommendations. The screen serves as a dedicated space for emotional self-awareness during pregnancy — empowering mothers to track and understand their mental and physical energy patterns over time.\n\n---\n\n## 3. Route\n\n```\n/mood-wellness\n```\n\n**Parent Navigation:** Library tab (push route)\n\n---\n\n## 4. Widget Name\n\n```dart\nMoodWellnessScreen\n```\n\n---\n\n## 5. Design Tokens\n\n### Color Palette (from DESIGN.md)\n\n| Token | Hex | Usage |\n|---|---|---|\n| `lavenderBloom` | `#7C3AED` | Primary brand, AppBar, chart lines |\n| `blushRose` | `#F9A8D4` | Mood emoji highlights, secondary accents |\n| `softMint` | `#6EE7B7` | Positive indicators, high energy states |\n| `morningMist` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n| `lavenderTint` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background |\n| `deepGraphite` | `#1F2937` | Primary text |\n| `stoneGrey` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, captions |\n| `mistyBorder` | `#E5E7EB` | Dividers, subtle structure |\n| `softCoral` | `#EF4444` | Error states |\n\n### Typography (Nunito — Google Fonts)\n\n| Style | Size | Weight | Usage |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `headlineMedium` | 24sp | 700 | Screen title |\n| `titleLarge` | 20sp | 600 | Section headers |\n| `titleMedium` | 16sp | 600 | Card titles |\n| `bodyLarge` | 16sp | 400 | Primary body text |\n| `bodyMedium` | 14sp | 400 | Secondary text, notes |\n| `labelLarge` | 14sp | 600 | Button labels, chip text |\n| `caption` | 12sp | 400 | Timestamps, metadata |\n\n### Spacing (8pt base grid)\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `xxs` | 4dp |\n| `xs` | 8dp |\n| `sm` | 12dp |\n| `md` | 16dp |\n| `lg` | 24dp |\n| `xl` | 32dp |\n\n### Corner Radius\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `sm` | 8dp |\n| `md` | 12dp |\n| `lg` | 16dp |\n| `full` | 999dp (pills) |\n\n---\n\n## 6. Layout Rules\n\n### Scaffold Structure\n\n```\nMoodWellnessScreen\n├── AppBar (\"Mood & Wellness\", back button, transparent/lavender tint bg)\n├── body: CustomScrollView\n│   ├── SliverAppBar (collapsible, pinned)\n│   │   └── Today's Mood Card (expanded height ~280dp)\n│   └── SliverToBoxAdapter\n│       ├── Mood Trend Chart Section\n│       ├── Energy Trend Chart Section\n│       └── Wellness Tip Section\n└── BottomNavigationBar: Hidden\n```\n\n### AppBar Behavior\n\n- **Title:** \"Mood & Wellness\", SemiBold 20pt, deepGraphite\n- **Leading:** Back arrow (IconButton, 48pt touch target)\n- **Background:** Transparent, blends into lavenderTint scaffold\n- **Scroll behavior:** SliverAppBar collapses on scroll; title remains visible\n\n### Body\n\n- `CustomScrollView` with `SliverAppBar` (no FAB per UX spec)\n- `SliverToBoxAdapter` wraps remaining sections below the collapsible header\n- Each section separated by 24dp vertical spacing\n\n### Bottom Navigation\n\n- **Hidden** on this screen (per UX.md 3.7)\n- Screen is reached via push route from Library tab\n\n---\n\n## 7. Sections\n\n### Section 1: Today's Mood Card\n\n**Description:** Large card with 5 emoji mood selectors in a horizontal row and an optional note field. The card serves as the primary interaction point for logging today's mood.\n\n**Widget Type:** `SliverAppBar` expanded child (Container card)\n\n**Layout:**\n```\nCard (rounded 16dp, morningMist bg, soft shadow)\n├── Header row: \"How are you feeling today?\" title + date\n├── Emoji row: 5 emoji buttons (😔 😕 😐 🙂 😊) evenly spaced\n├── Selected indicator: highlighted emoji with blushRose border\n└── Note field: optional TextField for context\n```\n\n**Emoji Mapping:**\n| Emoji | Mood Score | Label |\n|---|---|---|\n| 😔 | 1 | Terrible |\n| 😕 | 2 | Bad |\n| 😐 | 3 | Okay |\n| 🙂 | 4 | Good |\n| 😊 | 5 | Great |\n\n**Data Requirements:**\n- Reads `todayMood` from `MoodEntryProvider`\n- Writes new mood log on emoji tap via `MoodEntryProvider.logMood(score)`\n- If mood already logged today, show the selected emoji pre-highlighted\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Tap emoji → `MoodEntryProvider.logMood(score)` + visual highlight\n- Tap note field → expands for text input (max 200 characters)\n- Tap outside deselects note field\n\n**States:**\n- **Default:** No mood logged today, all emojis neutral\n- **Logged:** Selected emoji highlighted with blushRose border and subtle scale\n- **Loading:** Emoji tap shows 200ms ripple before confirmation\n\n---\n\n### Section 2: Mood Trend Chart\n\n**Description:** Line chart showing 7-day mood score history. The chart is interactive — tapping a data point reveals a bottom sheet with that day's details.\n\n**Widget Type:** CustomPaint line chart inside a Card container\n\n**Layout:**\n```\nCard (rounded 16dp, morningMist bg)\n├── Section header: \"Mood Trend\" + toggle chips (1W / 1M / All)\n├── Chart area: 200dp height, CustomPaint line chart\n│   ├── X-axis: 7 day labels (Mon, Tue, Wed, etc.)\n│   ├── Y-axis: 1-5 scale with emoji labels\n│   └── Line: lavenderBloom colored, 2dp stroke, smooth curve\n├── Legend: \"Score\" label + 5-dot color guide\n└── Tap target: entire chart is tappable\n```\n\n**Data Requirements:**\n- Reads `MoodEntryProvider.entries` last 7 days (filtered by `date`)\n- Mood scores 1-5 mapped to emoji at Y-axis positions\n- Data points connected with smooth bezier curves\n\n**Toggle Behavior:**\n- `1W` — Last 7 days (default)\n- `1M` — Last 30 days (shows more data points)\n- `All` — All historical entries\n- Active toggle has lavenderBloom bg at 15% opacity\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Tap data point → bottom sheet with day detail (date, mood score, emoji, note if exists)\n- Toggle chip tap → re-renders chart with new time range\n\n**Chart Style:**\n- Line color: `lavenderBloom` (#7C3AED)\n- Line stroke: 2dp\n- Data point dots: 6dp circles at each entry\n- Empty state: \"No mood data yet\" centered text\n\n---\n\n### Section 3: Energy Trend Chart\n\n**Description:** Line chart showing 7-day energy level history. Structure mirrors the Mood Trend Chart but tracks energy instead of mood.\n\n**Widget Type:** CustomPaint line chart inside a Card container\n\n**Layout:**\n```\nCard (rounded 16dp, morningMist bg)\n├── Section header: \"Energy Trend\" + toggle chips (1W / 1M / All)\n├── Chart area: 200dp height, CustomPaint line chart\n│   ├── X-axis: 7 day labels\n│   ├── Y-axis: 1-5 scale with energy descriptors\n│   └── Line: softMint (#6EE7B7) colored, 2dp stroke\n├── Legend: \"Energy\" label + 5-dot color guide\n└── Tap target: entire chart is tappable\n```\n\n**Data Requirements:**\n- Reads `MoodEntryProvider.entries` last 7 days\n- Energy levels 1-5 mapped to descriptors at Y-axis positions\n\n**Y-Axis Labels:**\n| Score | Label |\n|---|---|\n| 1 | Very Low |\n| 2 | Low |\n| 3 | Moderate |\n| 4 | High |\n| 5 | Very High |\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Tap data point → bottom sheet with day detail (date, energy level, note if exists)\n- Toggle chip tap → re-renders chart with new time range\n\n**Chart Style:**\n- Line color: `softMint` (#6EE7B7)\n- Line stroke: 2dp\n- Data point dots: 6dp circles\n\n---\n\n### Section 4: Wellness Tip\n\n**Description:** Contextual recommendation card that analyzes recent mood/energy patterns and suggests a gentle wellness nudge.\n\n**Widget Type:** Card with expandable content\n\n**Layout:**\n```\nCard (rounded 16dp, morningMist bg)\n├── Header row: \"Wellness Tip\" title + lightbulb icon\n├── Tip text: Contextual recommendation (2-3 sentences)\n├── Category badge: \"Mood\" / \"Energy\" / \"General\" chip\n└── Expand trigger: Tap anywhere on card to expand\n```\n\n**Tip Generation Logic (Rule-Based):**\n- If average mood < 3 over past 7 days → \"Your mood has been low lately. Consider a gentle breathing exercise or a short walk outside.\"\n- If average energy < 3 over past 7 days → \"Your energy levels seem to be dipping. Remember to stay hydrated and take short breaks throughout the day.\"\n- If mood is high but energy is low → \"You've been feeling good emotionally, but energy is lagging. Listen to your body and rest when needed.\"\n- Default → \"Regular mood check-ins help you notice patterns. Keep up the great work tracking your wellness!\"\n\n**Data Requirements:**\n- Reads `MoodEntryProvider.entries` last 7 days\n- Computes average moodScore and average energyLevel\n- Selects appropriate tip from static catalog\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Tap card → expands to show full recommendation (up to 100 characters additional detail)\n- Tap category badge → no action (informational only)\n\n**States:**\n- **Collapsed:** Shows tip preview (max 2 lines)\n- **Expanded:** Shows full tip text with additional context\n- **No Data:** Shows generic tip \"Log your mood to receive personalized wellness tips.\"\n\n---\n\n## 8. Data\n\n### Entity: MoodEntry\n\n```dart\nclass MoodEntry {\n  final DateTime date;\n  final int moodScore;    // 1-5 scale\n  final int energyLevel;  // 1-5 scale\n  final String? note;\n}\n```\n\n### Provider: MoodEntryProvider\n\n**Read Operations:**\n- `todayMood` → MoodEntry? — Today's mood entry (if exists)\n- `entries` → List<MoodEntry> — All mood entries sorted by date\n- `entriesInRange(start, end)` → List<MoodEntry> — Entries within date range\n\n**Write Operations:**\n- `logMood(int score)` → void — Logs/updates today's mood score\n- `logEnergy(int level)` → void — Logs/updates today's energy level\n- `addNote(String note)` → void — Adds/updates note for today\n\n### Screen Data Dependencies\n\n| Section | Data Source | Fields Used |\n|---|---|---|\n| Today's Mood Card | `MoodEntryProvider.todayMood` | `moodScore`, `note` |\n| Mood Trend Chart | `MoodEntryProvider.entriesInRange` | `date`, `moodScore` |\n| Energy Trend Chart | `MoodEntryProvider.entriesInRange` | `date`, `energyLevel` |\n| Wellness Tip | `MoodEntryProvider.entries` (last 7 days) | `moodScore`, `energyLevel` |\n\n---\n\n## 9. Motion\n\n### Entry Animations\n\n| Element | Animation | Duration | Curve |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| Today's Mood Card | Fade + slide up | 300ms | easeOut |\n| Mood Trend Chart | Fade + slide up (staggered 50ms after card) | 300ms | easeOut |\n| Energy Trend Chart | Fade + slide up (staggered 50ms after mood chart) | 300ms | easeOut |\n| Wellness Tip | Fade + slide up (staggered 50ms after energy chart) | 300ms | easeOut |\n\n### Micro-Interactions\n\n| Interaction | Animation | Duration | Curve |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| Emoji tap | Scale to 95% + color fill | 200ms | easeOut |\n| Toggle chip select | Background color fade | 150ms | easeInOut |\n| Card expand | Height + content fade | 250ms | easeInOut |\n| Chart data point tap | Scale pulse on dot | 200ms | easeOut |\n\n### Page Transitions\n\n- **Enter:** Push from Library tab — 300ms slide from right + fade\n- **Exit:** Swipe-back or back button — 300ms slide to right + fade\n\n---\n\n## 10. Accessibility\n\n### Semantics Labels\n\n| Element | Semantics Label |\n|---|---|\n| Mood emoji 😔 | \"Terrible mood, tap to log\" |\n| Mood emoji 😕 | \"Bad mood, tap to log\" |\n| Mood emoji 😐 | \"Okay mood, tap to log\" |\n| Mood emoji 🙂 | \"Good mood, tap to log\" |\n| Mood emoji 😊 | \"Great mood, tap to log\" |\n| Mood chart | \"Mood trend chart showing 7 day history\" |\n| Energy chart | \"Energy trend chart showing 7 day history\" |\n| Wellness tip card | \"Wellness tip: [tip text]\" |\n\n### Focus Order\n\n1. AppBar back button\n2. Today's Mood Card emoji buttons (left to right: 😔 😕 😐 🙂 😊)\n3. Note text field\n4. Mood chart toggle chips\n5. Energy chart toggle chips\n6. Wellness tip card\n\n### Contrast Notes\n\n- All text meets WCAG AA contrast (4.5:1 for body, 3:1 for large text)\n- Emoji buttons have 48pt minimum touch targets\n- Chart lines use lavenderBloom on morningMist — sufficient contrast\n- Focus indicators use 2dp blushRose outline\n\n---\n\n## 11. Anti-Patterns\n\n**DO NOT:**\n- Use default Flutter colors — all colors from design token palette\n- Add a FAB — this screen has no FAB per UX spec\n- Show BottomNavigationBar — it is hidden\n- Use sharp corners — all cards use 16dp radius\n- Display raw numbers on chart axes — use emoji/text labels\n- Use Inter or Roboto — Nunito only\n- Show gradients — flat colors only\n- Use touch targets smaller than 48pt\n- Place critical actions outside thumb zone","numLines":390,"startLine":1,"totalLines":390}}}
