119	
120	## 7. Sections
121	
122	### Section 1: Today's Mood Card
123	
124	**Description:** Large card with 5 emoji mood selectors in a horizontal row and an optional note field. The card serves as the primary interaction point for logging today's mood.
125	
126	**Widget Type:** `SliverAppBar` expanded child (Container card)
127	
128	**Layout:**
129	```
130	Card (rounded 16dp, morningMist bg, soft shadow)
131	├── Header row: "How are you feeling today?" title + date
132	├── Emoji row: 5 emoji buttons (😔 😕 😐 🙂 😊) evenly spaced
133	├── Selected indicator: highlighted emoji with blushRose border
134	└── Note field: optional TextField for context
135	```
136	
137	**Emoji Mapping:**
138	| Emoji | Mood Score | Label |
139	|---|---|---|
140	| 😔 | 1 | Terrible |
141	| 😕 | 2 | Bad |
142	| 😐 | 3 | Okay |
143	| 🙂 | 4 | Good |
144	| 😊 | 5 | Great |
145	
146	**Data Requirements:**
147	- Reads `todayMood` from `MoodEntryProvider`
148	- Writes new mood log on emoji tap via `MoodEntryProvider.logMood(score)`
149	- If mood already logged today, show the selected emoji pre-highlighted
150	
151	**Interactive Elements:**
152	- Tap emoji → `MoodEntryProvider.logMood(score)` + visual highlight
153	- Tap note field → expands for text input (max 200 characters)
154	- Tap outside deselects note field
155	
156	**States:**
157	- **Default:** No mood logged today, all emojis neutral
158	- **Logged:** Selected emoji highlighted with blushRose border and subtle scale
159	- **Loading:** Emoji tap shows 200ms ripple before confirmation
160	
161	---
162	
163	### Section 2: Mood Trend Chart
164	
165	**Description:** Line chart showing 7-day mood score history. The chart is interactive — tapping a data point reveals a bottom sheet with that day's details.
166	
167	**Widget Type:** CustomPaint line chart inside a Card container
168	
169	**Layout:**
170	```
171	Card (rounded 16dp, morningMist bg)
172	├── Section header: "Mood Trend" + toggle chips (1W / 1M / All)
173	├── Chart area: 200dp height, CustomPaint line chart
174	│   ├── X-axis: 7 day labels (Mon, Tue, Wed, etc.)
175	│   ├── Y-axis: 1-5 scale with emoji labels
176	│   └── Line: lavenderBloom colored, 2dp stroke, smooth curve
177	├── Legend: "Score" label + 5-dot color guide
178	└── Tap target: entire chart is tappable
179	```
180	
181	**Data Requirements:**
182	- Reads `MoodEntryProvider.entries` last 7 days (filtered by `date`)
183	- Mood scores 1-5 mapped to emoji at Y-axis positions
184	- Data points connected with smooth bezier curves
185	
186	**Toggle Behavior:**
187	- `1W` — Last 7 days (default)
188	- `1M` — Last 30 days (shows more data points)
189	- `All` — All historical entries
190	- Active toggle has lavenderBloom bg at 15% opacity
191	
192	**Interactive Elements:**
193	- Tap data point → bottom sheet with day detail (date, mood score, emoji, note if exists)
194	- Toggle chip tap → re-renders chart with new time range
195	
196	**Chart Style:**
197	- Line color: `lavenderBloom` (#7C3AED)
198	- Line stroke: 2dp
199	- Data point dots: 6dp circles at each entry
200	- Empty state: "No mood data yet" centered text
201	
202	---
203	
204	### Section 3: Energy Trend Chart
205	
206	**Description:** Line chart showing 7-day energy level history. Structure mirrors the Mood Trend Chart but tracks energy instead of mood.
207	
208	**Widget Type:** CustomPaint line chart inside a Card container
209	
210	**Layout:**
211	```
212	Card (rounded 16dp, morningMist bg)
213	├── Section header: "Energy Trend" + toggle chips (1W / 1M / All)
214	├── Chart area: 200dp height, CustomPaint line chart
215	│   ├── X-axis: 7 day labels
216	│   ├── Y-axis: 1-5 scale with energy descriptors
217	│   └── Line: softMint (#6EE7B7) colored, 2dp stroke
218	├── Legend: "Energy" label + 5-dot color guide
219	└── Tap target: entire chart is tappable
220	```
221	
222	**Data Requirements:**
223	- Reads `MoodEntryProvider.entries` last 7 days
224	- Energy levels 1-5 mapped to descriptors at Y-axis positions
225	
226	**Y-Axis Labels:**
227	| Score | Label |
228	|---|---|
229	| 1 | Very Low |
230	| 2 | Low |
231	| 3 | Moderate |
232	| 4 | High |
233	| 5 | Very High |
234	
235	**Interactive Elements:**
236	- Tap data point → bottom sheet with day detail (date, energy level, note if exists)
237	- Toggle chip tap → re-renders chart with new time range
238	
239	**Chart Style:**
240	- Line color: `softMint` (#6EE7B7)
241	- Line stroke: 2dp
242	- Data point dots: 6dp circles
